videos.headline: Engelland: Team wanted to get win for Las Vegas
videos.description: Golden Knights defenseman Deryk Engelland explains how much it means to the team that they won the home opener for the city of Las Vegas and what it meant to have the first responders on the ice before the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Interview (Engelland: Team wanted to get win for Las Vegas) 2017/10/10

videos.headline: Levy says Golden Knights pregame ceremony was 'powerful'
videos.description: Steve Levy explains what the atmosphere was like during the pregame ceremonies ahead of the Vegas Golden Knights' home opener and what has been so impressive about James Neal this season.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Levy says Golden Knights pregame ceremony was 'powerful') 2017/10/10 SC
